# BizSQL self-generated track: data/ is ignored globally, but the schema DDL and
# the blind (question, gold_sql) generation checkpoint are source-of-truth and
# MUST be committed for reproducibility (seed_bizsql_db.py reads schema.sql; the
# split step replays raw_pairs.jsonl without re-calling any LLM). The seeded
# .sqlite and the split dirs stay ignored — regenerated on demand.
!data/
data/*
!data/bizsql/
data/bizsql/*
!data/bizsql/schema.sql
!data/bizsql/raw_pairs.jsonl

